---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import StructuredData from '../../components/StructuredData.astro';
import { getAffiliateCTA } from '../../config/affiliate-links';
---

<Layout title="Fastest AI Website Builders (2025): Speed Comparison">
  <StructuredData type="WebPage" data={{ name: 'Fastest AI Website Builders', description: 'Which AI builder generates sites fastest? Durable wins at 30 seconds. Real speed testing, generation times, speed vs quality analysis.', url: 'https://aiwebsitebuilders.com/categories/fastest-ai-website-builders' }} />

  <section class="bg-[#FFF8F0] py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-5xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black">Fastest AI Builders:<span class="block text-[#F5521A]">Speed Test Results</span></h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mt-6">Need a site NOW? Real speed testing of AI generation times.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">Speed Rankings</h2>
      <div class="bg-orange-50 border-[3px] border-orange-400 rounded-xl p-6">
        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Durable:</strong> ~30 seconds (8.5/10) - <span class="text-[#F5521A] font-bold">FASTEST</span></li>
          <li><strong>Mixo:</strong> ~30-45 seconds (8.5/10)</li>
          <li><strong>Hostinger AI:</strong> ~45-60 seconds (7.9/10)</li>
          <li><strong>Dorik:</strong> ~60 seconds (8.1/10)</li>
          <li><strong>10Web AI:</strong> ~60-90 seconds (8.8/10)</li>
          <li><strong>Wix ADI:</strong> ~90 seconds (8.4/10)</li>
          <li><strong>Squarespace Blueprint:</strong> ~2-3 minutes (8.2/10)</li>
          <li><strong>Webflow:</strong> ~3-5 minutes (8.6/10)</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">Durable - The Speed King</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black">Durable</h3>
            <span class="bg-[#F5521A] text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-sm">30 seconds</span>
          </div>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Fastest AI Generation</p>
          <p class="text-sm mb-4">30 seconds from prompt to complete website with multiple pages, AI-written copy, images, contact form, CRM integration.</p>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-600 mb-4">Why so fast? Durable focuses purely on speed. Optimized AI for rapid generation.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-red-600">Tradeoff: Good designs, not stunning. Functional over beautiful.</p>
          {getAffiliateCTA('durable')}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">Speed vs Quality Tradeoff</h2>
      <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-[3px] border-yellow-400 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold text-yellow-800 mb-2">‚ö° Reality: Faster = Simpler</p>
        <p class="text-sm mb-4">The 30-second sites are functional, not amazing. Speed champions sacrifice design quality for velocity.</p>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <p><strong>Need it NOW:</strong> Durable. Fastest "good enough" option.</p>
          <p><strong>Can wait 2-3 minutes:</strong> Squarespace or Webflow. Significantly better results.</p>
          <p><strong>Best approach:</strong> Generate fast with Durable, then refine. Or use slow-but-better if time allows.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">What "Fast" Actually Means</h2>
      <div class="bg-red-50 border-[3px] border-red-400 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold text-red-800 mb-2">üö® 30-Second Generation ‚â† 30-Second Launch</p>
        <p class="text-sm mb-4">Even with Durable's speed, you'll spend time on:</p>
        <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
          <li>‚Ä¢ Reviewing generated content (10-15 minutes)</li>
          <li>‚Ä¢ Editing and customizing (30-60 minutes)</li>
          <li>‚Ä¢ Adding your branding (15-30 minutes)</li>
          <li>‚Ä¢ Setting up custom domain (10-30 minutes)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="font-bold text-red-800 mt-4">Reality: Expect 2-4 hours from start to publish-ready, even with fastest AI.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">Speed Test Results Table</h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full bg-white rounded-xl border-[3px] border-gray-200">
          <thead class="bg-gray-900 text-white">
            <tr><th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-bold">Builder</th><th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">Time</th><th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">Pages</th><th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">Quality</th><th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">Best For</th></tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Durable</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">30s</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">3-5</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-yellow-600">Good</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-sm">Urgent launches</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Mixo</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">30-45s</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">2-4</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-yellow-600">Good</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-sm">Landing pages</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Hostinger AI</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">45-60s</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">5+</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-yellow-600">Basic</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-sm">Budget sites</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">10Web AI</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">60-90s</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">5+</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">Excellent</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-sm">WordPress sites</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Squarespace</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-yellow-600">2-3m</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">5+</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">Excellent</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-sm">Beautiful sites</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Webflow</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-yellow-600">3-5m</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">3+</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">Outstanding</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-sm">Design quality</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">Recommendations</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-bold text-green-800 mb-2">üöÄ Need it TODAY (Within hours)</p>
          <p class="text-sm">Durable. Nothing else comes close for speed. 30 seconds to generated site, 2-4 hours to polished.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-bold text-blue-800 mb-2">üìÖ Have a week</p>
          <p class="text-sm">Take more time. Use 10Web, Squarespace, or Webflow for significantly better results. Speed difference doesn't matter.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-purple-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-bold text-purple-800 mb-2">‚öñÔ∏è Reality Check</p>
          <p class="text-sm">30 seconds vs 3 minutes doesn't matter in practice. Choose based on quality, not speed. You'll spend more time editing than generating.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
